        "readme": {
          "childMarkdownRemark": {
            "html": "<p>A plugin that lets you mark posts and drafts and automatically exclude them from production.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-it-works\"><a href=\"#how-it-works\" aria-label=\"how it works permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How it works</h2>\n<p>This plugin add a new field called <code class=\"language-text\">released</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">markdown</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">mdx</code> nodes. If your build happens before <code class=\"language-text\">date</code> of your post the <code class=\"language-text\">released</code> value will set to <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<h3 id=\"add-plugin-to-gatsby-nodejs\"><a href=\"#add-plugin-to-gatsby-nodejs\" aria-label=\"add plugin to gatsby nodejs permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Add plugin to <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-node.js</code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/*\n        ...\n    */</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-released'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"update-your-graphql-queries\"><a href=\"#update-your-graphql-queries\" aria-label=\"update your graphql queries permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Update your GraphQL queries</h3>\n<p>You may want to exclude drafts from a build step in file <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-node.js</code> and respect the <code class=\"language-text\">released</code> value from blog pages such as <code class=\"language-text\">index.js.</code></p>\n<p>In both cases the query will look something like this. Pay attention to a filter property.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> query <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">graphql</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n    {\n      allMarkdownRemark(\n        sort: { fields: [frontmatter___date], order: DESC }\n        filter: { fields: { released: { eq: true } } }\n      ) {\n        edges {\n          node {\n            id\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"update-your-component-code\"><a href=\"#update-your-component-code\" aria-label=\"update your component code permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Update your component code</h3>\n<p>This step is totally up to yours component tree. The key point is to request necessary fields via GraphQL query.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> query <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> graphql`\n  query <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">allMarkdownRemark</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token parameter\">sort<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fields<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>frontmatter___date<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> order<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">DESC</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      filter<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fields<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> released<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> eq<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          id\n          fields <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            slug\n            released\n            releasedNotForced\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-label=\"options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-released'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        fieldName<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'released'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        fieldNameNotForced<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'releasedNotForced'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        timezone<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'UTC'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        force<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> process<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>env<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">NODE_ENV</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> development\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"fieldname-and-fieldnamenotforced\"><a href=\"#fieldname-and-fieldnamenotforced\" aria-label=\"fieldname and fieldnamenotforced permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">fieldName</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">fieldNameNotForced</code></h3>\n<p>Use to overried the default field name.</p>\n<h3 id=\"force\"><a href=\"#force\" aria-label=\"force permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">force</code></h3>\n<p>In case you want to display posts in development mode you can use <code class=\"language-text\">force</code> option.</p>\n<h3 id=\"timezone\"><a href=\"#timezone\" aria-label=\"timezone permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">timezone</code></h3>\n<p>Set another timezone that will be respected at build time to calculate <code class=\"language-text\">released</code> value.</p>",
